com.tinkerpop.rexster.kibbles.frames

Class FramesExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.rexster.extension.AbstractRexsterExtension
      • com.tinkerpop.rexster.kibbles.frames.FramesExtension
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RexsterExtension

    public class FramesExtension
extends AbstractRexsterExtension
    An extension that exposes Tinkerpop Frames via Rexster. Configuration in rexster.xml looks like:

    com.tinkerpop.frames.domain.classes.Person com.tinkerpop.frames.domain.classes.Project
